data.description: Welcome this wonderful home in the heart of Merritt Island's Tropical Gardens subdivision! This beautifully remodeled residence is a great opportunity for first-time buyers looking for a move-in-ready haven. One or more photo(s) was virtually staged. Step inside to discover a nicely maintained home. The recently replaced roof ensures peace of mind, while a fresh interior paint job gives the entire home a modern and inviting feel. The bedrooms welcome you with brand-new carpeting. The spacious living room is excellent for gatherings, leading seamlessly to a beautiful kitchen adorned with new appliances. A formal dining room sets the stage for intimate dinners and special occasions. The family room beckons with sliding patio doors that open to your private patio and fenced-in yard. Whether it's a quiet evening under the stars or hosting friends and family, this space is ready for joyous moments. Nestled near the Osteen Park and the Intracoastal Waterway Park.
